<section class="success-page">
    <div class="success-card">
        <img src="/images/fresh-meat-logo.png" alt="프레시미트">
        <span class="success-badge"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 등록 완료</span>
        <h1>프레시미트 단골 등록이 완료됐습니다.</h1>
        <p>다음 방문부터 연락처로 단골 정보를 확인하고, 선택하신 취향에 맞춰 더 빠르게 추천해드릴게요.</p>
        <div class="reward-box">
            <div>
                <span>지급 포인트</span>
                <strong><%= points.toLocaleString() %>P</strong>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span>회원 유형</span>
                <strong><%= membershipType === 'prepaid' ? '선불 충전' : membershipType === 'subscription' ? '정기 구독' : '기본 단골' %></strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="success-actions">
            <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">상품 보러가기</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-light">홈으로</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.success-page {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 180px);
    padding: 60px 20px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: #f8f3ea;
}
.success-card {
    width: min(620px, 100%);
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 34px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(66, 42, 18, 0.08);
}
.success-card img {
    width: 110px;
    height: 82px;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin: 0 auto 14px;
}
.success-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    background: rgba(33, 79, 53, 0.1);
    color: var(--green);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
}
.success-card h1 {
    margin: 16px 0 10px;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
}
.success-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
}
.reward-box {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 24px 0;
}
.reward-box div {
    background: var(--paper);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
}
.reward-box span,
.reward-box strong {
    display: block;
}
.reward-box span {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
}
.reward-box strong {
    margin-top: 4px;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}
.success-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    justify-content: center;
}
@media (max-width: 540px) {
    .success-page { padding: 34px 16px; }
    .success-card { padding: 24px 18px; }
    .reward-box,
    .success-actions { grid-template-columns: 1fr; display: grid; }
}
</style>
